<li><a href="/wiki/Redressement_Fran%C3%A7ais" title="Redressement Français">Redressement Français</a>, a French technocratic movement founded by <a href="/wiki/Ernest_Mercier" title="Ernest Mercier">Ernest Mercier</a> in 1925</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Scientism" title="Scientism">Scientism</a></li>
