<li><i><a href="/wiki/The_Revolt_of_the_Masses" title="The Revolt of the Masses">The Revolt of the Masses</a></i>, a book by <a href="/wiki/Jos%C3%A9_Ortega_y_Gasset" title="José Ortega y Gasset">José Ortega y Gasset</a> containing a critique of technocracy</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Wealth,_Virtual_Wealth_and_Debt" title="Wealth, Virtual Wealth and Debt">Wealth, Virtual Wealth and Debt</a></i>,  a book by  Nobel prize-winning chemist <a href="/wiki/Frederick_Soddy" title="Frederick Soddy">Frederick Soddy</a> on monetary policy and society and the role of energy in economic systems</li></ul>
