<li id="cite_note-technocracy1-5"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-technocracy1_5-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-technocracy1_5-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite class="citation web"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20090422182206/http://www.technocracy.org/Archives/History%20%26%20Purpose-r.htm">"History and Purpose of Technocracy by Howard Scott"</a>. Technocracy.org. Archived from <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.technocracy.org/Archives/History%20&amp;%20Purpose-r.htm">the original</a> on 22 April 2009.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=History+and+Purpose+of+Technocracy+by+Howard+Scott&amp;rft.pub=Technocracy.org&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.technocracy.org%2FArchives%2FHistory%2520%26%2520Purpose-r.htm&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ATechnocracy" class="Z3988"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r951705291"/></span>
</li>
